Author: Pohky, NjalTheKnut
Name: Lewder Teleporter
Punchline: Chat Commands for Teleporting, now with a dash of spicy flavoring!
Description:
Adds Chat Commands to Teleport to Aetherytes or Areas by Name, and adds some optional ENF theatrics upon arrival.
e.g. /ltp Quarrymill or /ltpm South Shroud
Supports setting up an Alias for Aetherytes to be used with Teleporter Commands
e.g. /ltp home instead of /ltp Estate Hall (Free Company)
